2011-07-08T05:55:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/chroma-ate-inc-june-sales-fall-4-59-table-2360-tt.html
CHROMA ATE INC (2360)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 4.59% to NT$549,672,000 from NT$576,105,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            549,672          576,105    
YOY%              -4.59%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           3,158,335        2,673,832   
YOY%              18.12% 
=================================================================
 